    <item>
      <title>拉加德认为欧洲央行利率方向明确，步伐有待决定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/lagarde-sees-clear-direction-for-ecb-rates-pace-to-be-decided</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德表示，欧洲央行借贷成本的方向很明确，但降低成本的步伐仍有待决定，但她不排除采取更大幅度的举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/lagarde-sees-clear-direction-for-ecb-rates-pace-to-be-decided</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 14:56:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泽连斯基抨击腐败后乌克兰总检察长辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/ukraine-prosecutor-general-resigns-after-zelenskiy-blasts-graft</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰总检察长安德烈·科斯汀在对检察官获取虚假残疾证明的行为进行大规模调查后提出辞职，此举引起总统弗拉基米尔·泽连斯基的批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/ukraine-prosecutor-general-resigns-after-zelenskiy-blasts-graft</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 14:52:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长拉加德在关税面前捍卫公平贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-22/ecb-s-lagarde-defends-fair-trade-in-the-face-of-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行行长克里斯蒂娜·拉加德在回应美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普“关税”是他最喜欢的词时表示，公平贸易是“我们不应该抛弃的东西”。拉加德在与弗朗辛·拉夸的独家对话中发表了上述言论。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-22/ecb-s-lagarde-defends-fair-trade-in-the-face-of-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 14:51:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国央行行长贝利表示需要新的监控工具</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-22/boe-governor-bailey-on-need-for-new-reforms-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国央行行长安德鲁·贝利表示，需要新工具来密切关注非银行金融机构。央行已在系统范围内开展探索性方案。他在纽约彭博全球监管论坛上发表讲话。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-22/boe-governor-bailey-on-need-for-new-reforms-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 14:37:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>森特诺称若数据支持，欧洲央行将考虑进一步降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/ecb-would-mull-faster-cuts-if-data-suggests-this-centeno-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员马里奥·桑特诺表示，如果数据显示欧洲央行准备考虑加大货币宽松力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/ecb-would-mull-faster-cuts-if-data-suggests-this-centeno-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 13:57:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织下调全球增长预测，警告风险加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/imf-lowers-global-growth-forecast-warns-of-increasing-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织下调了明年全球经济增长预测，并警告称，战争、贸易保护主义等风险正在加剧，但同时该组织也赞扬各国央行抑制了通胀，而没有让各国陷入衰退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/imf-lowers-global-growth-forecast-warns-of-increasing-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科特迪瓦收成回升，可可期货延续下跌趋势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/cocoa-futures-extend-slide-as-ivory-coast-harvest-picks-up</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球最大可可种植国科特迪瓦的港口可可交货量增加，缓解了供应紧张局面，可可期货跌至两周来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/cocoa-futures-extend-slide-as-ivory-coast-harvest-picks-up</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 12:09:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东停火谈判持续，油价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-october-22</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易商关注以色列和伊朗之间的紧张局势，且尽管美国努力斡旋停火，但双方的袭击仍在继续，油价因此上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-21/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-october-22</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 21 Oct 2024 23:25:48 GMT</pubDate>
